channel.title: 7 Compile Errors
channel.description:
Okay so i've just done this tutorial: [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,451186.0.html]Demise's Clickable Stat Leveling[/url]
And I get 7 errors when I did that last part. Errors:
[code] src\server\model\players\packets\BankX2.java:27: error: cannot find symbol int level = amount; ^ symbol: variable amount location: class BankX2 src\server\model\players\packets\BankX2.java:49: error: cannot find symbol int level = amount; ^ symbol: variable amount location: class BankX2 src\server\model\players\packets\BankX2.java:71: error: cannot find symbol int level = amount; ^ symbol: variable amount location: class BankX2 src\server\model\players\packets\BankX2.java:93: error: cannot find symbol int level = amount; ^ symbol: variable amount location: class BankX2 src\server\model\players\packets\BankX2.java:115: error: cannot find symbol int level = amount; ^ symbol: variable amount location: class BankX2 src\server\model\players\packets\BankX2.java:137: error: cannot find symbol int level = amount; ^ symbol: variable amount location: class BankX2 src\server\model\players\packets\BankX2.java:159: error: cannot find symbol int level = amount; ^ symbol: variable amount location: class BankX2 Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 7 errors Press any key to continue . . . [/code]
Help please!
